---
title: Pan-Fried Cod with Crushed New Potatoes, Green Beans and Tarragon Sauce
description: For a recipe that delivers on flavour and speed, this simple but delicious dish comes out on top. Light and delicate in flavour, cod is a great fish to pair with this mild and creamy tarragon sauce. We’ve served it alongside crushed new potatoes and crunchy green beans for an easy and nutritious weeknight dinner. Tonight, you’re allowed to fish for compliments!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/pan-fried-cod-1664a31c-47d8a4b4.jpg
